      • enableLatePlugins

        public static void enableLatePlugins()

      • enableEarlyPlugins

        public static void enableEarlyPlugins()

      • reload

        public void reload()
        Reload all subsystems and the whole of canary. Don't over-use this method, it slows down the server. It is used by the reload command and should not be used by anything else!
